    <briefdescription>
<para>A collection of filters for Spatial Anchor queries. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Filters that have been set will be combined via logical conjunction. E.g. results must match the ids filter AND fall within the radius constraint when both have been set.</para>
<para>This struct must be initialized by calling <ref refid="group___spatial_anchor_1ga366c74107d4e7696ea4609902d75966b" kindref="member">MLSpatialAnchorQueryFilterInit</ref> before use.</para>
